      WITH FRAME F-Main IN WINDOW W-Win.
  ENABLE RECT-1 BUTTON-aceptar BUTTON-cancelar FILL-PDBASE COMBO-PROTOCOLO 
         FILL-SERVIDOR BUTTON-VERIFICA BUTTON-ayuda 
      WITH FRAME F-Main IN WINDOW W-Win.
